<br>
I find it hard to believe I am that unlucky but in all the fights before and leading up to Agnarr I used it and rogues were sending me tells saying they were having to back off and evade 10 times more than normal when I use BoC/Blackout or even my Emp Ssra 2hs. I like the stats on it and would like to use it but I have very serious doubts on tanking a boss mob with it now after last night since I got people killed before changing back to duel wield. Just want to hear others comments on SRC if you have one and let me know if that was just my bad luck or is this a piece of crap. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=91997" target="top"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://xtctripp101.homestead.com/files/sigs/Brudal_sig.gif" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
