<br>
So if you main hand a BoC, it really doesn't do much to add to that hate.<br>
<br>
I have fairly good luck with a Double Edged Stormblade in main hand and the FB3 shield off hand. The blade has a 150dd proc that procs a lot. If I am add tank, I have no trouble getting and keeping aggro. When I tank a boss mob, I usually dual wield with BoC offhand to get initial aggro, then swap in the shield and have no issues. I also take significantly less damage.<br>
<br>
Use of the shield for maximum effectiveness is situational. I can keep aggro in an exp group with 2 monks and a rogue, but it is a bit harder and it means the others have to watch their aggro more.<br>
<br>
